					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thanks to my beta readers <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/liv3r" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3365104&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509585780" alt="Liv3r" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3365104)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/liv3r" >Liv3r</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509585780" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" >OthellotheCat</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ghostchibi" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1382994&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509585780" alt="ghostchibi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1382994)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ghostchibi" >ghostchibi</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leveritas" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1558990&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509585780" alt="Leveritas" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1558990)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leveritas" >Leveritas</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509585780" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bananarepublic" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2788421&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509585780" alt="BananaRepublic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2788421)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bananarepublic" >BananaRepublic</a></span>.</p> <p>I realize that some people might prefer to leave how Fuller lost the Circus a mystery, but this was always how it happened in my mind so I figured it should be added to Dread &amp; Circuses.</p> <p>I'm also aware that Tom is a designated villain. He's not a bad guy, he's just in opposition to my protagonists, and he doesn't really deserve all the shit he's been through. Protagonists just aren't always good guys.</p> <p>This tale also references some characters in BananaRepublic's Fuller series Green Day. He's just posted <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/green-day-ii">Green Day II</a> so check it out and keep an eye open for a couple Dread &amp; Circuses references in it.</p> 
				 	]]>
